description: Flights between the Isle of Man and Guernsey are stopped after a cluster of seven coronavirus cases.
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man - Guernsey air bridge suspended after Covid-19 cases
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man - Guernsey air bridge suspended after Covid-19 cases - BBC News
maintext: Mr Ferbrache said of the move: "I don't think they've overreacted, I think we may well have taken the same decision if the boot had been on the other foot, but it is a suspension... they want it lifted as soon as possible."
